{"tid":1290432,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"ALL IN US] ITZY討論區(5) 期待第一個綜藝 7月回歸大發","createTime":"2019-07-06T13:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T05:32:00.000Z","uid":40895,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c403c32f0a45ab5cda0636dbbcd0003c1fd685","tid":1290432,"uid":40895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/053805_fbe9258f98afc48055712fcfdb8e4d7c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F053805_fbe9258f98afc48055712fcfdb8e4d7c.png&h=992fd0b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dxmq6gYVAAUISE-.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDxmq6gYVAAUISE-.jpg%3Aorig&h=a35138c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dxmq7hEUwAAiAyU.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDxmq7hEUwAAiAyU.jpg%3Aorig&h=61b24fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DxrxmslV4AEmy7s.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDxrxmslV4AEmy7s.jpg%3Aorig&h=193428bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dxrxnp5UYAMLbEn.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDxrxnp5UYAMLbEn.jpg%3Aorig&h=9d710373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nITZY（韓語：있지；日語：イッジ），為韓國JYP娛樂旗下的五人女子團體。由五名韓國成員禮志、Lia、留真、彩領、有娜組成，2019年2月12日以首張單曲專輯《IT'z Different》正式出道。在JYP娛樂與GOT7，和前Wonder Girls成員宥斌、惠林同為二本部。團名意味著粉絲、大眾所盼望的一切，ITZY全都具備（EVERYTHING YOU WANT<strong> IT'Z</strong> IN US.），並把這樣的抱負濃縮成短而有力的口號「有嗎？有啊！」，就此形成了兼具特色與氣勢的團名。問候語為：「All in Us！大家好，我們是ITZY。」同時雙手比出剪刀手連在一起，形成反Z，翻轉形成Z的手勢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>每日睇一萬次專區！</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://